Reasoning: The previous formula produced None values after recalculation, likely because LibreOffice did not evaluate the IFERROR/IF construct correctly when the referenced previous row contains header text. To avoid any subtraction involving non‑numeric header values, we can compute the usage only when the previous row has the same Serial Number *and* the previous Weight is numeric. We'll use ISNUMBER to guard the subtraction and wrap the whole expression in IFERROR. The formula will be:

